response.original_title: Walking the Length of England - Adventure Documentary
response.overview: Last summer I set off on an adventure to walk the length of England, a route that would take me 50 days to complete and have me hiking 800+ miles in total.  This is the adventure movie version of my adventure series walking the length of England. I wild camped and hiked the entire length of England from Land's End to Carter's Bar on the boarder of Scotland.
